Comment: 1. Nc3 is a very odd opening, considered by the world of chess experts to be too passive and therefore a weak choice, virtually never played at serious levels. I had no idea what to do with it, so I winged it, and turns out, I picked just about the worst possible "good" response, giving white a decent opening and a strong attack.
